&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Is there a particular order to the afternoon activities? Let's see what questions we can ask to get learners really thinking about the text.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</contents>
