&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Once students organize themselves, ask the whole class:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;When does Choua take her brother and sister to the playground?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Do they do homework before going to the playground? Why?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;When do you think they wash clothes? Is it every day? Every other day? Once a week?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;How is Choua's life different? How do we know?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Why do you think she likes her new schedule?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
